- $\alpha = 1.0$: all predicted negative → TPR = FPR = 0 → point (0, 0)
- $\alpha = 0.0$: all predicted positive → TPR = FPR = 1 → point (1, 1)

The curve always goes from (0, 0) to (1, 1).

:::

